title: Stock Car Extreme v1.38 + extras [noSteam] [online/offline]
description:
Stock Car Extreme v1.38 (internal build 1.6)
--------------------------------------------

Multilanguage



About this Jimbus edition:
-------------------------

- Custom installer highly compressed.
- The game is updated to 1.38 version.
- Some of the best cars and tracks made by fans are included.
- Nothing has been deleted.



Instructions:
-------------

1. Run "setup.exe" to install the game.
2. Always start the game with the file "GSC_Loader.exe" or use the shortcuts the installer creates.
 
Q: Does the multiplayer work?
A: Yes, it does.

Q: Do I need Steam to play?
A: No, you do not.

Q: Does it work under Windows 10?
A: Yes, it does.



Notice this is not an update but the full game. Do not install it over an existing installation.


Thanks to all the people of cs.rin.ru who made this possible
